{"tid":1769473,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撐曼聯連登仔反應大 梁凱晴笑籲不割席不分化","createTime":"2019-12-05T02:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T04:03:53.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0d0986afd6ee0a8f1b394f501a3d917558d2be","tid":1769473,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"在宣佈參選當晚即遇襲、當選觀塘月華選區區議員的梁凱晴，不但深得香港「連登仔」喜愛，同時獲日本傳媒高度關注。對於網民封稱的「港版綾瀨遙」外號，她笑言：「網民實在太抬舉我喇，有啲好似貶低咗綾瀨遙嘅感覺。」她形容自己「只係普通女仔」，可能因為香港的女性從政者較少，較易引人留意，對此她覺得「有好有唔好」，最希望當然是大眾着重其地區工作和理念。<br />\n<br />\n既然深受「連登仔」愛戴，梁凱晴會否與「連登巴絲」connect？她指自己一直有連登、高登的戶口，只不過沒有覆文。有關不少人留意到她喜歡英超球隊曼聯，因此引起非曼聯球迷「好大反應」，梁凱晴打趣指，自己只是支持一支隊球，大家毋須「割席」，笑謂：「唔好因為球隊就分化。」<br />\n<br />\n中學時代的梁凱晴曾經加入少年警訊服務團；畢業於嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院的她是律政司司長鄭若驊、行會成員羅范椒芬的師妹，對於鄭若驊這位師姐，梁坦言「完全失望」，譬如修例一事上，不同界別人士都曾建議當局完善《逃犯條例》修訂，可惜「佢（鄭）完全冇聽到意見，就一味話係唔可行」，「其實係咪真係冇彎轉到呢個餘地呢？佢一路都好似林鄭咁樣唔聽民意。」梁續指，「我哋學校就係要『一心一道』嘅教訓，佢（鄭）完全做唔到一個榜樣畀其他師妹」，如今只能奉勸師姐問責下台。"},{"pid":"dec03e7f3d58dc2b0c4820866918d7cb9fcc0879","tid":1769473,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c828d5409e30c9d6bd5825ce14cdb87b58247dda","tid":1769473,"uid":1206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"一個政治人物因為非政治野而出鏡太多 感覺上會有DD危險<br />\n希望佢做得順順利利"},{"pid":"727d2ffa0383857fd699c0b2c46e0c9005ecfc6b","tid":1769473,"uid":9116,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獌? 不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191205/large/1575477984_b7e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575477984_b7e2.png&h=ca880945&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會睇波既都係好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de849a99fdb6c119016fff0c5b39948b6caf3d3","tid":1769473,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:22:10.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=48864af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</span></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"85360b4cd483bd50b6c7942b6dab838b58327ae9","tid":1769473,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"專注返地區工作先"},{"pid":"f6545d9a29efd2f8520ecbc7c09fdd293ba94e8f","tid":1769473,"uid":76776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6986504edf3949bbebfdd2e6718dda32a2bc98b","tid":1769473,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"搞睇波團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07297480bd48d8d9f09c674a6cae042bd32c428a","tid":1769473,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://upload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F28%2FFlYKWb.png\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/cUk5jd6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUk5jd6.jpg&d=nBH2CsHB%2BC